# Web Scraping Using BeautifulSoup

## Description
This project demonstrates how to scrape data from a website using Python,
BeautifulSoup, and requests, and store the extracted data in a CSV file.

## Website Used
https://quotes.toscrape.com (Scraping practice site)

## Tools
- Python
- BeautifulSoup
- requests
- CSV

## Features
- Fetch HTML content
- Parse and extract quotes
- Extract author and tags
- Handle missing elements
- Save data to CSV

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install requests beautifulsoup4
2. Run the script:
   python web_scraper.py

## Outcome
Intern can collect data from web sources using BeautifulSoup.
